Class VadereProject

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScenarioFinishedListener

    public class VadereProject
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScenarioFinishedListener
    A VadereProject holds a list of ScenarioRunManagers and functionality to manage them.
